{"tid":1579843,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好亂叫炒車","createTime":"2019-09-18T18:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T06:15:31.000Z","uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c937ca99b4674c6199fc1b337d006a1ef8cd4f","tid":1579843,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:49:29.000Z","msg":"有證據證明傳聞係錯先叫炒<br />\n假設例子：鏡頭影住黑警拉人，跟住傳聞被捕人士A 係中學生，然後A嘅朋友、同學主動出嚟講A原來係大學生，呢啲先叫炒<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺性暴疑雲、太子打死人疑雲、密集嘅個別被自殺疑團等等，只要冇證據證明傳聞係錯，就唔叫炒車<br />\n<br />\n可以證明炒車證據例子(如有)：<br />\n1. 新屋嶺人士全部話自己冇受虐待<br />\n2. 太子cctv影住個個傷者都自己識行路<br />\n3. 有人證明到佢前一日自殺者仲在生、有人目擊自殺個一刻"},{"pid":"5a4d6fac8af47d69fe0b8cf8da39387679162133","tid":1579843,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a651f6c0256a8816dbfe6a8215e82828208b3d","tid":1579843,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d17ca5cffc090acd0f9b18aac20611b8fc8604","tid":1579843,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1580455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1580455/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.22 香港連儂牆日</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n921 星期六何妖發起清連儂牆行動，大家同小朋友出入時請注意安全。之但係咁，They only know how to destroy, but<span style=\"color: red;\"> we know how to build</span> 所以響度正式發起 9.22 建設香港連儂牆 2.0<br />\n打工仔好善用公司資源啦~~~~<br />\n同日有機場測試，人力分散，大家萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n另外，個人認為<span style=\"color: red;\">9.21 應集中火力響元朗，回顧7.21</span>，宜早不宜晚，<br />\n唔知大家點睇，尤其擔心沙田柚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20D0Lr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20D0Lr3.jpg&h=52e1469e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}